  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nIt looks like `@truffle/hdwallet-provider` does not wok in the browser.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nTry doing `const HDWalletProvider = require('@truffle/hdwallet-provider');` in the browser, in an app bundled with Webpack.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThat import will work.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nWhen I try to do so, I get the error:\r\n\r\n```\r\nUncaught TypeError: Cannot read property 'toString' of undefined\r\n```\r\n",
